Comment: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:12.65,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:12652,12652}Intro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:33952,36052}Why don't you play with us, Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:37686,38819}I'm Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:41919,44619}If you're looking for\NKobayakawa Rumi, that'd be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.61,0:00:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:44619,48919}You're like two peas in a pod.\NWhy don't you help people tell you apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:48919,49852}Help how?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:49852,53719}Like, wear some name tags,\Nor put a big mark on your foreheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:53719,56886}Don't be ridiculous.\NJust learn it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:56886,61086}It reminds me, there is someone\Nwho can always tell you apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:62786,66252}It is none other than the lovely\NTouma Katsuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:69186,71252}See you later!\NSorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89552,93352}I'm glad that we took today's hike\Nseparately from the men's club.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93352,95286}Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95286,97519}I know about Touma-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97519,99486}I could hear you back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103152,105452}Ruka, would you like\Nto go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105752,107386}S… Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115852,116752}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122219,125286}I felt so embarrassed\Nto have you as my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125286,127986}You ran away without\Nso much as a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127986,129752}Rumi, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130086,133086}You wanted to keep it\Nfrom me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133086,134519}I understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134519,138719}You knew I was in love with him\Nand wanted to spare me the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145286,148452}Come here, girls!\NWe'll look for a shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164686,167519}Rumi, about what you said earlier…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167519,169452}Oh, you're still thinking about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169452,172086}It's frustrating,\Nbut I'll let you have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174652,176486}You'll have to give him\Na proper answer later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176486,178019}That you'll date him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178786,180219}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190752,192752}No way! These are human bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192752,194086}Oh my God!\NI'm so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194086,198319}We learned about these in history class.\NIt's one of these ancient mass burial sites…{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198319,200052}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200052,202619}Don't scream! Don't scream.\NIt's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202619,205219}We'll leave here\Nas soon as the rain passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207352,209052}Senpai? Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209686,211252}She's… She's dead…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232719,235486}{\i1}I knew there was something strange\Nabout this musty air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250119,251619}Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256886,259452}{\i1}I can't… move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264386,265686}{\i1}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265686,268552}{\i1}That's right.\NIt's like you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268552,269919}{\i1}I'm going to die anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269919,273819}{\i1}I should've told\NTouma-senpai that I loved him.
