Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373952,374686}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374686,376652}Thank goodness.\NShe's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376652,377686}Call the doctors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377686,380586}Ah, you were in a coma for 3 days!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380586,381486}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381486,383252}No, you should stay in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383252,384086}Where's Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384086,384852}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384852,386752}Rumi woke up yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386752,389086}We were worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389086,391286}You two are the only ones\Nwho were saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391886,394019}Just the two of us…\NThat graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394886,397552}I'm so sorry for these girls.\NTo die of a shock…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397552,400019}But we never stopped having hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400019,401219}Of a shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401219,404952}Well, they didn't sustain any trauma.\NThe doctors can't think of anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404952,406119}But that's all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406119,410519}We hid in some old tomb, and the air there\Nwas so fetid… we felt bad soon after…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410519,411919}Ah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411919,415686}After the rescue action, the police\Nwent further in to investigate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415686,416952}but they found nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417386,420319}That's not possible!\NTell them, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422886,425252}Come on, tell them\Nabout that terrible stench.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425552,427186}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428519,431552}{\i1}The newspaper only reported\Nthat the girls died of a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431552,435952}{\i1}The discovery of the burial site got covered\Nwithout being linked to this incident
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435952,438519}{\i1}in a small note on a third page.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446786,449452}Anyway, we're resuming\Nthe club activity from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450386,453886}Kobayakawa twins and Asako\Nare now the only girls on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453886,456286}You'll train with the boys\Nfor time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457186,459352}I see that not everyone\Nmade it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459352,460652}– Ishikura!\N– Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460652,462252}Tell the news to the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462252,463552}All right, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466352,467352}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468019,469086}Touma-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474252,475686}I'm so glad you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480486,482419}Let me take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485519,489352}{\i1}S… Senpai… talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499052,501052}All right, kids!\NThat's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501919,504186}Let's clean this place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514852,516852}Oh, I didn't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518186,519286}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521552,525586}It's better that you don't get used\Nto being close with the boys team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525586,527886}A lot of stuff may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527886,529686}You're such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529686,530986}What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530986,533952}I'm just openly saying what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533952,535852}Let me hear it again, Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536919,539019}You don't even know\Nhow to recognize your rival in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539019,542152}I'm Rumi, not Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543452,546052}You're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554852,557986}I won't let anybody\Nspeak to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557986,560152}What's your problem?\NLet go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605686,607286}{\i1}Asako-senpai…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628019,628852}Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630186,633086}What are you standing there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633086,635686}Rumi, Asako-senpai… she just…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635686,636886}Did you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636886,640052}Of course I did.\NIt's all over school.{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642019,643419}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643419,646519}I'm washing my hands.\NWhat else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646519,648552}But it serves her right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648552,651452}She was nothing but making eyes\Nall day long with the boys from our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651452,652786}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654186,655252}Let me say this, Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657019,659019}If you don't want to end up like her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660186,662686}you better stay off\NTouma-senpai as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667886,669219}{\i1}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669219,671519}{\i1}There's no way you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671519,674119}{\i1}What made you\Nchange so much, Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678086,680819}{\i1}After that,\Nnothing happened for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680819,683786}{\i1}Rumi has not changed\Never since, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683786,688119}{\i1}Could these terrible events\Nfade with time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692819,695619}{\i1}I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695619,699552}{\i1}I couldn't accept like everyone that\Nmy friends' deaths were caused by a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703619,705186}What are you afraid of?\NThat's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705186,706186}Senpai…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706186,708219}I came to ask for your reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708219,709486}I'm Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709486,712219}I could never mistake you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713019,713686}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714452,717086}I know what you've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717086,719919}But it wasn't easy for me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719919,722152}I'm okay if you hate my guts.\NJust tell it to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722686,725619}{\i1}I love you.\NI'm so in love with you! But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728986,731652}I see. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732019,733086}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733586,735086}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735386,739219}Were you looking\Ninto this case alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739219,741386}I couldn't help it. I mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741386,745519}This story is essentially\Nidentical to the Tutankhamun's curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745786,747752}Tutankhamun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747752,750052}He was an ancient\NEgyptian pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750052,751352}It's a well-known story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751352,756152}Most of the people involved in the excavation\Nof his tomb have died in mysterious ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756152,759452}This phenomenon caused quite a commotion\Nand media named it a "curse of the pharaohs".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759452,761286}Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761286,764219}Did these people really die\Nbecause of a curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764219,767219}They made it up, right?\NThere's no way it could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769619,772986}Such questions are best answered\Nfrom an objective point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772986,774186}Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774186,777319}I will investigate this thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777319,779386}Don't worry about it\Nuntil I have more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779852,780819}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780819,782986}Don't be late\Nfor the morning training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800619,801919}Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804152,805586}I told you to stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806019,808086}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808086,810186}What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810186,811886}I don't know that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812286,814086}But I've got to say…\NIt's so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815419,817586}You disregarded my warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818286,820552}Now you'll share Asako's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820552,822019}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833052,833852}Stop it, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877286,879619}You fell off the emergency stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879619,881252}How the hell has that happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881252,882319}Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883186,885419}Why didn't you go the normal way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885419,887252}What were you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887252,889252}It's the Tutankhamun's curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889252,890319}It's the same…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890719,891986}Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893852,895186}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896852,898986}There's way too much\Ngoing on lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898986,900686}And you're in the center of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914086,915386}Touma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915386,916952}I didn't expect you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917052,919386}Well, I heard everything\Nfrom one of the club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920452,922119}Thank you for visiting our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922119,926586}But I'd like her to stay in a hospital\Nfor a while, until her abrasions heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926586,927886}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930719,932352}That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932352,935019}I thought she fell from the fifth floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935019,936552}It's nothing short of a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936552,938786}I'm just glad she's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938786,940452}I'll be on my way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940686,942352}It's okay. You can stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942352,944152}No, I have something to do.{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945452,946619}All right. See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947652,949619}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952019,953819}I'll walk him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953819,954486}Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954486,955952}Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956852,957552}Let her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958919,961719}Mom.\NI can't go back to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961919,963186}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963819,966252}If I come home, I'll get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966252,967386}By Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967386,969819}No, that's not Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969819,972252}That's not the kind Rumi we knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974952,976686}Ruka's acting weird recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976686,977952}So I noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977952,979952}She seems to be\Nobsessed with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979952,982286}We're twins, but we're worlds apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982286,983852}Which one do you like more, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983852,985819}You like me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985819,988919}I guess.\NYou have much in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988919,991919}{\i1}It's only confusing to have\Ntwo things that are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998152,998919}Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002352,1003886}I think I sprained my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004952,1006852}Are you okay? Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007419,1009552}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010119,1013552}Please, help me get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013552,1016986}There's nobody inside.\NAll the way to my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016986,1017986}That's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018586,1019952}You'd do that for Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022319,1024886}What's your problem?\NWhat is it that Ruka has and I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025152,1027319}What is it… Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027319,1031819}Ruka would never pretend\Nthat she sprained her ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060986,1062186}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062186,1063352}Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063352,1065952}{\i1}I'm calling you so late, I hope\Nyou don't get yelled at by any nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065952,1067952}{\i1}I stayed all night up.{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067952,1069852}{\i1}Did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069986,1071819}No. I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072352,1075852}Actually, I have something to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075852,1077919}My dad is a novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077919,1079952}His name's Touma Yuichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079952,1082019}Well, it's okay if you don't know him.{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082019,1084386}Anyway, he lent\Nsome historical records.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084386,1087186}Some of them write in great detail\Nabout the Tutankhamun's curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087186,1090819}They also investigate the causes of death\Nof the people involved with the tomb excavation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091486,1095186}As expected, it was no curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095186,1099519}Well, nothing got ever officially confirmed.\NBut if we trust this book's author—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103586,1105186}Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106586,1109219}Senpai, don't spend\Ntoo much time in these books.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109219,1111052}Rumi?! Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111052,1113352}What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113719,1115819}The better question is,\Nhow can I do such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118319,1121219}Katsuyuki-san, I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121719,1123852}{\i1}Where does she have\Nthis strength from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130286,1131586}The line's busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133519,1137219}Get off me, Rumi.\NI don't like being pushed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137552,1138919}I'm Ruka, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139286,1141852}If you don't stop it this instant,\NI'll get really pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141852,1143386}I love you, Katsuyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145852,1147252}Get ahold of yourself, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147252,1149519}You may look the same,\Nbut your hearts are nothing alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150119,1151752}You're entirely different people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152552,1154919}Ruka must be worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154919,1158719}This is perfect.\NYou should listen to this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159852,1162119}Hey, dude!\NWhat is going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162686,1165219}Takashi!?\NDon't open the door! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169319,1171319}What? It's just you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171319,1172752}How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173286,1177352}I heard a girl's voice.\NI thought you brought someone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177352,1178919}Don't be stupid.\NIt was just the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178919,1180919}I'm on the phone\Nwith someone. Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181086,1183886}Ah, so that's where you hid your girl.\NAll right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188419,1191419}This is all getting\Njust way too spooky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191419,1192819}But still…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194152,1195552}Hello? This is Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196419,1197486}Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197486,1199352}Ruka? Rumi was here moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199352,1200186}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208219,1212419}{\i1}Yes… she can fly in the sky\Nand blends into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216419,1219786}Yes. I'd be happy\Nif you were with me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219786,1222119}Is that right?\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222119,1223219}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233052,1233952}Fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251252,1255919}Why don't we see how Touma-senpai\Nis going to feel if there's only one of us left?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255919,1257019}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257019,1258052}No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258052,1259752}Let's hug a little longer.{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273419,1275219}I guess that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275219,1278319}I wish you\Na warm welcome in heaven.{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283419,1284286}So hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312852,1313619}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313619,1314886}Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314886,1316019}You have to jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316019,1318452}From here?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318452,1320286}If you don't want to die,\Nyou'll have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320286,1321519}I'll catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322152,1323486}I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325486,1327786}Jump! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1354952,1356986}Ruka… I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356986,1357786}It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363419,1364486}Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364486,1365852}See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366319,1369552}I bet it was the same\Nwith that emergency staircase.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369552,1371552}Ruka has the same powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372119,1374519}You may have the same disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1381086,1382952}That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382952,1384152}Katsuyuki-kun.{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1384152,1387519}If your theory is correct,\Nwe should immediately see the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387519,1390452}I am sorry I woke you up\Nin the middle of the night, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1390452,1391686}Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1391686,1394686}But I gotta say, like father, like son.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399086,1401786}This man is my father's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1401786,1403819}What was that about a disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1404452,1407419}Well, that only matters\Nif you believe the book I've read.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407419,1409619}I was trying to tell you\Nabout it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409619,1414819}It wasn't a curse that the people who dug\Nthe Tutankhamun's grave died to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1414819,1416752}It suggests that the cause\Nmight have been a bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1417186,1418886}A bacteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1418886,1424919}In my opinion it's pretty plausible that\Nthe tomb you hid in had a similar bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.91,0:23:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1424919,1429986}It killed everybody when you inhaled it,\Nbut in your case, it gave you special powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1429986,1434186}It is a bacteria that do not exist\Nin the present day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1434186,1436286}Thus, you were infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1436286,1437019}Infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1437019,1439386}But how come\Nthat we alone survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1439719,1443819}My theory is that the two of you\Nwere born with antibodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1443919,1446886}Antibodies?\NHow convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1446886,1450819}So the people who further investigated\Nthe site also had these antibodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.45,0:24:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1451452,1456419}It might be the case that this bacteria\Ndoesn't survive long in contact with fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.41,0:24:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1456419,1459752}That's probably the reason\Nwhy the rescue party was unaffected.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.75,0:24:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1459752,1461986}Cool. I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1463986,1468019}I'm only in love with you, Touma-san.\NWhy can't you see past Ruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.01,0:24:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1468019,1468952}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.95,0:24:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1468952,1470952}I… love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.35,0:24:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1472352,1474819}Rumi, please go back\Nto who you were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.75,0:24:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1475752,1476886}What happens if I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.25,0:24:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1487252,1488286}How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.28,0:24:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1488286,1489552}Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.55,0:24:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1489552,1492186}Their blood was confirmed\Nto contain unknown bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.18,0:24:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1492186,1495452}I was unable to see it under the microscope,\Nbut there was a chemical reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.45,0:24:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1495452,1497519}It might be a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.51,0:25:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1497519,1500252}Can you find a way to treat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1500252,1502352}I don't know anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.35,0:25:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1502352,1506219}But I will concentrate on finding whatever\NI can that'll keep their symptoms down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.75,0:25:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1506752,1509452}In any case,\Nwe've already got something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.45,0:25:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1509452,1510886}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.88,0:25:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1510886,1512119}{\i1}Sun's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.95,0:25:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1524952,1528252}{\i1}We can go back\Nto being close sisters again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.25,0:25:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1528252,1535819}{\i1}The hope that it was possible brought light\Nto our hearts, which were shrouded in darkness.
Comment: 0,0:25:44.68,0:25:44.68,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1544686,1544686}Ending
Comment: 0,0:28:16.68,0:28:16.68,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1696686,1696686}Next episode preview
