Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.68,0:28:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1705686,1711319}Ruka, who learned of Rumi's intense love\Nfor Katsuyuki, decides to turn him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.31,0:28:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1711319,1713652}Furthermore,\Nshe notices a relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.65,0:28:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1713652,1716386}between Rumi's unusual behavior\Nand current moon's phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.38,0:28:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1716386,1720052}She asks Rumi to go to the hospital\Nto run another test.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.05,0:28:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1720052,1723086}But something is going to happen\Nto Ruka in that hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.18,0:28:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1723186,1727152}"The Darkness of the Sea,\Nthe Shadow of the Moon", Volume 2:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.15,0:28:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1727152,1730186}"A Nightmarish Premonition".\NPlease look forward to it!
